### About me
My name is Kostas (short for Konstantinos). I am a web application developer, and I hail from Greece although I now live in the Netherlands. My hobbies are reading and travelling amongst others which I have no time to do.

### My work
I've worked on projects for a long time and below are some of the most notable ones.
- Internal portal CRM for Lely
- Internal management console for Irdeto
- Online BV creation for Firm24
- Wrapping a digital gift for WrapTheGift
